{"id":561923,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/06/【图说天朝】不良信息发现技巧/","date":"2017-06-23T08:33:52Z","modified":"2017-06-23T21:47:27Z","title":"【敏感瓷】“不良信息发现技巧”","content":"<p>@ZhangDajun：某地网警受训要针对的的敏感词，请墙内人尽量避免使用。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-561972\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/DC5WPenWAAAUCXm.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"415\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/DC5WPenWAAAUCXm.jpg 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/DC5WPenWAAAUCXm-300x207.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/DC5WPenWAAAUCXm-768x531.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>1.关键词查找法：</p>\n<p>（1）涉政治类关键词，如：你国、GCD、中共、国豚、药丸、月饼、贵支、你支、支那、党山、兔杂、五毛、毛粉、8平方等涵污蔑性的隐晦词语；</p>\n<p>（2）涉重点节点关键词，如：月饼、二胎等；</p>\n<p>（3）涉民族宗教类的关键词，如：绿教、回虫、回子、MSL等；</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/DC5WPenXcAEPHXQ.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-561973\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/DC5WPenXcAEPHXQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"386\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/DC5WPenXcAEPHXQ.jpg 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/DC5WPenXcAEPHXQ-300x193.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/DC5WPenXcAEPHXQ-768x493.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>（4）特指国家领导人的隐晦关键词，如：恁大、习包子、今上、背书名、某大大、恁麻、恁蔴、李大鸟、李中堂、中堂大人、李博士、李竞强、蛤蟆、王73等；</p>\n<p>（5）和网络赌博、网络色情有关的关键词，如：果聊、敲背、艾薇等；</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18270,18269,10466,21627],"tags":[32940,13446,32941,9283,15122]}